OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCrumbling schools hit by   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fleaks and cold, BBC finds  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Schools in urgent need of repair have  
OL,6, told Panorama they are struggling to   
OL,7, keep children warm in buildings that   
OL,8, are "not fit for purpose".             
OL,10,FAt one primary in Devon, temperatures  
OL,11,Fare so low that children keep gloves   
OL,12,Fand coats on during some lessons.      
OL,14,FThe head teacher says despite parts of 
OL,15,Fthe school being seemingly impossible  
OL,16,Fto heat, he has been told it does not  
OL,17,Fqualify for extra money for repairs.   
OL,19,FThe Department for Education (DfE) says
OL,20,Fpupil and staff safety is "paramount". 
